hadiths[138]{hadithnumber,text}:
2175,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo shakhs ham mein se nahin hai jo kisi aurat ko uskey shohar ke khilaf ubhaare ya ghulam ko uskey Malik ke khilaf kar dey.''"
2176,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''koi aurat apni (deeni) behan ki Talaq ka mutalba na karey ke is tarah uska piyala (apni khatir) khaali kara ley. usey chahiye ke nikah kar ley, usko wohi kuch milega jo uskey liye muqaddar kiya gaya hai.''"
2177,"Mahaarib (bin Disaar) kehtey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ne Talaq se badh kar naa-pasandida kisi chiz ko halal nahin farmaya.''"
2178,"Mahaarib bin Disaar Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ke yahan halal kamon mein sab se naa-pasandida kaam Talaq hai.''"
2179,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke zamaney main apni biwi ko Talaq de-di jabkey wo ayyame-haiz mein thi. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne iskey baarey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha to aapney farmaya : ''usko hukm do ke us se ruju karey, phir usko apney yahan rakhey yahan tak ke wo paak ho, phir usey haiz aaye , phir paak ho, phir agar chahey to usey biwi banaey rakhey ya chahey to Talaq dey dey (magar) mubashrat se pehley. aur yehi wo iddat hai jiskey mauqe par Allah taala ne aurton ko Talaq deney ka hukm diya hai.''"
2180,Janab Naafe bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne apni biwi ko eik Talaq de-di jabkey wo ayyame-haiz mein thi. ... . aur (mazkura baala) hadees Malik ki tarah riwayat ki.
2181,"Saalim, Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat kartey hain ke unhoney apni biwi ko ayyame-haiz mein Talaq de-di to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se iska zikr kiya. aapney farmaya : ''usey hukm do ke us se ruju karey, phir jab paak ho to Talaq dey ya jab wo hamal se ho.''"
2182,"Salim bin Abdullah apney walid (Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma)) se riwayat kartey hain ke unhoney apni biwi ko Talaq de-di jabkey wo haiz se thi. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne iska zikr Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se kiya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) naraz huey, phir farmaya : ''usey hukm do ke us se ruju karey, phir usey rokey rakhey yahan tak ke wo paak ho jaey, phir haiz aaye aur paak ho. tab agar chahey to usey Talaq dey jabkey wo paak ho, mubashrat se pehley. yehi wo iddat ke mauqe par Talaq hai jis ka Allah taala ne hukm diya hai.''"
2183,Yunus bin Jubair kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se puchha tha ke aapney apni biwi ko kitni talaaqein di thin? unhoney kaha : eik.
2184,"Yunus bin Jubair kehtey hain, maine Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se puchha ke eik aadmi ne apni biwi ko Talaq de-di jabkey wo ayyame-haiz mein thi. to unhoney kaha : tum ibne-Umar ko jantey ho? maine kaha : haan. unhoney kaha ke Abdullah bin umr ne apni biwi ko uskey haiz ke dino mein Talaq dey di. to umr (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaye aur un se daryaft kiya, to aapney farmaya : ''usey hukm do ke us se ruju karey, phir iddat ke shuru mein Talaq dey.'' Yunus kehtey hain : maine kaha : kya ye Talaq shumar hogi ? kaha : to aur kya? bhala agar wo aajiz rahey (ke sahih hukm na maloom kar sakey) ya ahmaq-pan ka izhar karey (ghalat tareeqey se Talaq dey dey? to kya uski ye Talaq fuzul aur bekar jaeygi?)"
2185,"Abdur-Rehman bin Aiman maula Urwa ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se sawal kiya aur Abu-Zubair sun rahey they. kaha ke aap ka us shakhs ke baarey mein kya khayal hai jisney apni biwi ko haiz ke dino mein Talaq di ho? unhoney kaha ke Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke zamaney main apni biwi ko haiz ke dino mein Talaq de-di thi. to umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se kaha ke Abdullah bin umr ne apni biwi ko Talaq de-di hai halanke wo haiz se hai. to Abdullah ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us biwi ko mujh par lauta diya aur usey kuch na samjha. aur farmaya : ''jab ye paak ho jaey to phir Talaq dey ya rok ley.'' ibne-Umar kehtey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne (is tarah) padha : (يا أيها النبي إذا طلقتم Nisa فطلقوهن في قبل عدتهن)''aey Nabi ! jab tum apni aurton ko Talaq dena chaho to unhen unki iddat ke shuru mein Talaq do. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke is riwayat ko Yunus bin Jubair , Anas bin Sirin , Saeed bin Jubair , Zaid bin Aslam , Abu-Zubair aur Mansoor ba-waasta Abu-Waeil ne ibne-Umar se riwayat kiya hai. aur in sab ki riwayaat ka mafhoom eik hi hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey hukm diya ke ruju kar lo yahan tak ke wo paak ho jaey, phir chaho to Talaq dey do aur chaho to rok lo. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : aisey hi Muhammad bin Abdur-Rehman ne ba-waasta Saalim, ibne-Umar se riwayat kiya hai. lekin Zohri ( ba-waasta Salim (aur Naafe ki riwayaat jo ibne-Umar se hain in mein hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unko ruju kerney ka hukm diya yahan tak ke paak ho jaey, phir haiz aaye phir paak ho, phir chahey to Talaq dey dey ya rakh ley. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : Ata Khuraasaani se bhi ba-waasta (الحسن  ، عن ابن عمر) isi tarah riwayat ki gaee hai jaisey ke Naafe aur Zohri ne riwayat ki hai. aur ye sab riwayaat Abu-Zubair ke bayan ke khilaf hain."
2186,Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu Anhuma) se sawal kiya gaya ke eik aadmi apni biwi ko Talaq deta hai aur phir us se mubashrat kar leta hai magar Talaq deney ya us se ruju kerney par gawah nahin banata. unhoney kaha : to ne khilafe sunnat Talaq di aur khilafe sunnat hi ruju kiya. biwi ko Talaq detey waqt gawah banao aur ruju ke waqt bhi. aur phir aisey na karna.
2187,"Abu-Hasan maula bani Nofal ne Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se puchha ke ghulam jiski zojiyat mein koi londi ho, wo usey do talaaqein dey dey , phir wo dono iskey baad azad ho jaeyn to kya is azad ghulam ke liye munasib hai ke wo is (apni pehley wali biwi , yani ab azad londi) ko shaadi ka paigham dey? unhoney kaha : haan . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne isi tarah faisla farmaya tha."
2188,"Janab Ali (bin Mubarak) ne apni sanad se mazkura baala hadees ki manind bayan kiya magar (حدثني) ka seegha istimal nahin kiya (balke (عن(an)) kaha. Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne kaha : terey liye eik hi (Talaq) bach gaee hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne yehi faisla kiya tha. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain ke maine Imam Ahmed bin Hanbal (Rahimahullah) ko suna, unhoney kaha : Abdur-Razzaaq ne bayan kiya ke ibne Mubarak ne Maamer se puchha : ye Abul-Hasan kon hai? usney bahut bada, bhari pathar uthaya hai. (ye adam aitimaad ka izhar hai.) Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke ye Abul-Hasan wohi hai jis se Zohri riwayat kartey hain. Zohri kehtey hain ke ye fuqaha mein se tha. aur Zohri ne us se kaee ahadis riwayat ki hain. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : Abul-Hasan maroof hai magar is hadees par amal nahin hai."
2189,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan karti hain ke aapney farmaya : ''londi ke liye do talaaqein hain aur iskey ''quru'' (iddat) do haiz hai. Abu-Aasim ne kaha : mujhey Mazahir ne ba-waasta Qasim , Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se isi ke jaisi riwayat kiya magar lafz ye they : (وعدتها حيضتان) . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke ye majhool hadees hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke in dono hadeeson par amal nahin hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : is sanad mein Mazahir naami raawi maroof raawi nahin hai."
2190,"Amr bin Shuaib apney walid (Shoaib) se aur wo apney dada ( Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma)) se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Malik baney baghair Talaq nahin, Malik baney baghair azad karna nahin, aur Malik baney baghair farokht nahin. ibne Sabaah ne ye izafa bhi bayan kiya : ''aur Malik baney baghair kisi nazar ka pura karna nahin.''"
2191,"Abdur-Rehman bin Haris ne ba-waasta Amr bin Shuaib iski sanad se (Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) sey) mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani riwayat kiya aur mazeed kaha : ''jisney kisi gunah (nafarmaani) aur gunah ke kaam par qasam uthaai ho, uski qasam nahin, aur jisney qata' rehmi ki qasam uthai ho, uski qasam nahin.''"
2192,is mein itna izafa hai ke wohi nazar manna durust hai jiskey zikr se Allah taala ki raza maqsood ho.
2193,"Muhammad bin Ubaid bin Abi Saleh jo eliya (baitul-Maqdis) mein rehtey they kehtey hain ke main Adi bin Adi Kandi ke sath mein rawana hua yahan tak ke ham Makka pahunch gaey. isliye unhoney mujhey Safiya binte Sheba ke yahan bheja. usney Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se (bahut kuchh) yaad kiya hua tha. usney kaha ke maine Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ko kehtey huey suna, wo farmati thin ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aap farmatey they : ''ighlaaq mein Talaq nahin aur na ghulam ko azad karna hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain : (الغلاق) (aur (غلاق) merey khayal mein ghazab aur ghussey ke maani mein hai."
2194,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''teen baaten aisi hain agar koi unko haqeeqat aur sanjeedagi mein kahe, to haqeeqat hain aur hansi mazaak mein kahe , to bhi haqeeqat hain. nikah, Talaq aur (Talaq sey) ruju.''"
2195,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke aayat kareema : (والمطلقات يتربصن بأنفسهن ثلاثة قروء ولا يحل لهن أن يكتمن ما خلق الله في أرحامهن) ''Talaq wali aurten apney aap ko teen haiz tak rokey rakhen aur unhen halal nahin ke wo wo chiz chupa lein jo Allah ne unke rahmon mein paida ki hai.'' iski tafseer mein bayan kiya ke aadmi jab apni biwi ko Talaq deta tha to wohi uski taraf ruju kerney ka ziyada haq daar samjha jata tha, chahey teen talaaqen hi dey chuka hota. usko mansookh kar diya gaya aur farmaya : (الطلاق مرتان)'' (qabile ruju) Talaq do baar hai.''"
2196,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Abde-Yazeed . ... jo Rukaana aur iskey bhaiyon ka walid tha. ... . usney Umme- Rukaana ko Talaq de-di aur qabeela muzena ki eik aurat se nikah kar liya. phir ye (Muzni aurat) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aai aur kaha : ye merey kaam ka nahin, jaisey ye baal, aur usney apney sar se baal pakad kar ishara kiya (yani naa-mard hai), aap merey aur uskey darmiyan alehdgi kara den. is par Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ghussa aaya aur phir Ruknaana aur uskey bhaiyon ko bulwaya , aur haazirin se kaha : ''kya dekhtey ho ke falan bachcha us se kis qadr mushabeh hai. ''yani Abde-Yazeed ke sath'' aur falan us se kitna mushabeh hai?'' sab ne kaha ke ji haan (yani jab pehley uski aulad mojud hai to us aurat ka da'wa kis tarah sahih ho sakta hai) to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Abde-Yazeed se farmaya : ''usko Talaq dey do.'' chunanche usney (Talaq) dey di. aur farmaya : ''apni (pehli) biwi se jo Rukaana aur uskey bhaiyon ki maa hai, ruju kar lo.'' wo kehney laga : aey Allah ke Rasool ! maine usey teen talaaqein di hain. aapney farmaya : ''mujhey maloom hai, us se ruju kar lo.'' aur ye aayat tilawat farmaai : (يأيها النبي إذا طلقتم Nisa فطلقوهن لعدتهن) ''aey Nabi ! jab tum aurton ko Talaq dena chaho to iddat ke waqt Talaq diya karo. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Naafe bin Ajeer aur Abdullah bin Ali bin Yazid bin Rukaana ki riwayat hai ke Rukaana ne apni biwi ko Talaqe-batta di thi to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uski biwi ko us par lauta diya tha, ye riwayat ziyada sahih hai, kyonkey ye us aadmi ki aulad hain aur ghar waley uskey mutalliq ziyada ba-khabar ho saktey hain, yani Rukaana ne apni biwi ko batta Talaq di aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usko eik bana diya."
2197,"Mujahid kehtey hain ke main Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke paas baitha tha ke eik shakhs unke paas aaya aur kehney laga ke maine apni biwi ko teen talaaqein de-di hain. chunanche wo khamosh hi rahey yahan tak ke mujhey guman hua ke wo us aurat ko is par wapis kar dengey. (ruju kerney ka fatwa dey dengey.) phir boley : tum main eik uthta hai aur himaqat ka irtikab karta hai, phir kehta hai : ibne-Abbas ! ibne-Abbas ! tehqiq Allah taala ne farmaya hai : (ومن يتق الله يجعل له مخرجا) ''jo Allah ka taqwa ikhtiyar karey, Allah uskey liye nikalney ki raah bhi paida farma deta hai.'' tu ne Allah ka taqwa ikhtiyar nahin kiya, lihaza mein terey liye koi raah nahin paata. to ne apney Rab ki nafarmani ki aur biwi tujh se juda hogi. aur Shan wale Allah ne farmaya hai : (يأيها النبي إذا طلقتم Nisa فطلقوهن  في قبل عدتهن) ''aey Nabi ! jab tum aurton ko Talaq dena chaho to unhen unki iddat ke shuru mein Talaq do.'' (is sanad ki mutaabiaat ka bayan) (1) Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke is hadees ko (A) Humaid Aaraj waghaira ne ba-waaste Mujahid, ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat kiya hai. (B) Shoba ne Umra bin Murra se ba-waaste Saeed bin Jubair , ibne-Abbas se riwayat kiya hai. (C) Ayub aur ibne-Juraij ne Ikrima bin Khalid se ba-waaste Saeed bin Jubair , ibne-Abbas se riwayat kiya hai.(D) Ibne-Juraij ne Abdul-Hameed bin Raafe se ba-waaste Ata, ibne-Abbas se riwayat kiya hai. (E) Aamash ne ba-waaste Malik bin Haris, ibne-Abbas se riwayat kiya hai. (F) Ibne-Juraij ne ba-waaste Amr bin Dinar, ibne-Abbas se riwayat kiya hai. ye sab riwayat kartey hain ke ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne teen Talaq ko nafiz kiya aur kaha aurat tujh se (baaina) juda ho gaee jaisey ke (إسماعيل an أيوب an Abdullah بن كثير) ki sanad mein aaya hai. (2) Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha ke Hammad bin Zaid , Ayub se ba-waaste Ikrima, ibne-Abbas riwayat kartey hain ke jab kehney waley ne eik hi martaba kaha ke ''tujhey teen Talaq hai'' to ye eik Talaq hai. aur Ismail bin Ibrahim ne Ayub se ba-waaste Ikrima se usey naqal kiya to ibne-Abbas ka naam nahin liya balke isko Ikrima ka qaul banaya hai."
2198,"Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ka ye fatwa badal gaya tha jaisey ke hamein Ahmed bin Saleh aur Muhammad bin Yahya ne bayan kiya. ... aur ye riwayat Ahmed bin Saleh ki hai. ... aur un dono ki sanad yun hai : (حدثنا عبدالرزاق an معمر an Zohri an أبي سلمة بن عبدالرحمن بن عوف) (doosri sanad) (Muhammad bin Abdur-Rehman bin Soban, Muhammad bin Iyaas se bayan kartey hain ke hazraat ibne-Abbas, Abu-Huraira aur Abdullah bin Amr bin Al-Aas (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum) se sawal kiya gaya ke kunwari ladki ko agar uska shohar teen talaaqein dey dey (qabl az mubashrat) to? sab ne kaha ke ye shohar ke liye halal nahin yahan tak ke kisi aur se nikah karey.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Imam Malik (Rahimahullah) ne ba-sanad (يحيى بن سعيد an بكير بن الأشج an معاوية بن أبي عياش) riwayat kiya (Muawiya ne kaha) ke main is qissey ka gawah hun, Muhammad bin Ayas bin Buker, ibne Zuber aur Aasim bin umr ke paas aaya aur in dono se is baarey mein sawal kiya to unhoney kaha ke ibne-Abbas aur Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum) ke paas chaley jao, maine unko Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan chhoda hai. phir ye qissa bayan kiya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka ye qaul ke aurat teen Talaq se apney shohar se baaina (juda) ho jati hai, chahey shohar ne us se mubashrat ki ho ya na ki ho, wo uskey liye halal nahin rehti jab tak ke kisi aur se nikah na kar ley. unka ye fatwa aisey hi hai jaisey ke unhoney bai sirf ( soney chaandi ki bai (ke baarey mein fatwa diya tha, phir ibne-Abbas ne apney is fatwey se ruju kar liya tha."
2199,"Taaoos kehtey hain ke Abul-Sahba'a naami eik shakhs Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se bahut ziyada sawal kiya karta tha. usney kaha : kya aap ko ilm hai ke jab koi aadmi apni biwi ko mubashrat se pehley teen talaaqein dey deta tha to aisi Talaq ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam), Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke daur se pehl eik hi banaya (shumar) kartey they? ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne kaha : haan ! aadmi jab apni biwi ko mubashrat se pehley teen talaaqein dey deta tha to ehade-risaalat, ehade-Abi Bakr aur ibtadaaey ehade-Umar mein isko eik hi bana detey they. umr ne jab dekha ke log musalsal talaaqein deney lagey hain to unhoney kaha : unhen in par nafiz (laagu) kar do."
2200,"Ibne Taaus apney walid se bayan kartey hain ke Abul-Sahba'a ne Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se kaha : kya aap jantey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke zamaney mein , abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke ehad aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki amaarat ke ibtidaai (shuruati) teen saal tak teen talaaqon ko eik banaya ( shumar kiya ( jata tha? to ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne kaha : haan !"
2201,Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' aamaal ka daromadar niyat par hai. insan ke liye wohi hai jo usney niyat ki ho. so jisney hijrat ki Allah aur uskey Rasool ki taraf to uski hijrat Allah aur uskey Rasool ki taraf hai aur jisney duniya hasil kerney ke liye hijrat ki ya kisi aurat ke liye ke us se shaadi kar ley to uski hijrat usi ki taraf hai jiski taraf usney hijrat ki hai. ''
2202,"Janab Abdullah bin Kab apney walid Kab bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ke qaaid they jabkey wo na-bina ho chukey they. kehtey hain ke maine Kab bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se suna aur tabuk wala waqia bayan kya. bayan kya ke jab pachas mein se chaalis din guzar gaey to achcha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka peghambar aaya aur kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tumhen hukm detey hain ke apni biwi se alehda ho jao . maine puchha : usey Talaq de-dun ya kya karun? kaha : nahin, balke us se alehda raho, uskey qarib mat hona. chunanche maine apni biwi se kaha : apney ghar walon ke paas chali jao aur unhi ke paas raho , yahan tak ke Allah tabarak w taala us maamley mein koi faisla farma dey."
2203,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ham ko ikhtiyar diya to ham ne aap hi ko ikhtiyar kya tha, chunanche usko kuch bhi shumar na kya gaya."
2204,"Hammad bin Zaid ne bayan kya ke maine Ayub se puchha : aap ko kisi ka ilm hai jo ( أمرك بيدك ( '' tera maamla terey haath mein hai'' ki tafsil mein Hasan ( Basri) ki tarah kehta ho? ( unka bayan agli riwayat mein aa raha hai. ( Ayub ne kaha : nahin magar wohi jo ham ko Qatada ne b-sanad kaseer maula ibn Samra sey, abu-Salma sey, unhoney Hazrat Abu-Huraira sey, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se uski manind bayan kya. Ayub ne kaha : phir kaseer maula ibn Samra hamarey paas aaye to maine un se (us riwayat ke mutalliq ( puchha . to unhoney kaha : ''maine ye kabhi bayan nahin kya. '' phir maine unki ye baat Qatada se kahi to unhoney kaha ke bayan to kya hai magar bhool gaey hain."
2205,Qatada . ... Janab Hasan Basri (Rahimahullah) se bayan kartey hain ke) أمرك بيدك ( '' tera maamla terey haath mein hai. '' ye teen talaaqein hoti hain.
2206,"Naafe bin Ajeer bin Abd Yazid bin Rukana se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rukana bin Abd Yazid ne apni biwi Suhema ko bitta Talaq dey di. phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko uski khabar di aur kaha : qasam Allah ki! maine us se eik hi ka irada kya tha, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qasam se! to ne sirf eik hi ka irada kya tha?'' Rukana ne kaha : Allah ki qasam! maine sirf eik hi ka irada kya tha. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uski biwi ko us par lota diya. chunanche usney usko dusri Talaq Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke daur mein aur teesri Talaq Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke daur mein di. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke us riwayat ka ibtidaai (shuruati) hissey Ibrahim bin Khalid kalbi ke alfaz hain aur aakhiri ibne-Sarah ke ."
2207,"Muhammad bin Yunus Nasai apni sanad se Naafe bin Ajeer sey, wo Rukana bin Abd Yazid sey, wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se yehi hadees bayan kartey hain."
2208,"Abdullah bin Ali bin Yazid bin Rukana apney walid se wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke unhoney apni biwi ko bitta Talaq de-di thi. phir wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaya to aapney puchha : ''tum ne kya irada kya tha ?'' usney kaha : eik ka . aapney kaha : ''Allah ki qasam se kehtey ho? ''kaha : Allah ki qasam se kehta hun. aapney farmaya : ''ye wohi hai jo tum ne irada kya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke ye riwayat ibne-Juraij ki) pichhley ( riwayat ( 2196 ( se sahih tar hai ke Rukana ne apni biwi ko teen talaaqein di thin kyonkey ye log uskey apney ghar waley hain, aur ye uskey mutalliq behtar jantey hain. aur ibne-Juraij ki riwayat abu-Raafe ke kisi bete ne Ikrima se aur usney ibne-Abbas se riwayat ki hai."
2209,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain ke aapney farmaya : ''bila-shuba Allah azz-w-jall ne meri ummat se wo batein maaf farma di hain jinkey mutalliq unhoney guftgu na ki ho ya amal na kya ho, aur wo jiskey mutalliq mehaz dil mein khayal aaya ho.''"
2210,Abu-Tamima Hujaimi se riwayat hai ke eik shakhs ne apni biwi ko kaha : aey behan ! to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya ye teri behan hai?'' pas aapney is andaze-guftgu ko napasand kya aur us se mana farmaya.
2211,"Abu-Tameema ne apni qom ke eik shakhs se riwayat kya ke usney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna. jabke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik shakhs ko suna ke wo apni biwi ko keh raha hai : aey behan! to aapney usko us se mana farma diya. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain (ke is hadees ki do sandaein aur bhi hain) (1) Abdul-Azeez bin mukhtaar Khalid sey, wo abu-Usman sey, wo Abu-Tameema sey, wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se. (2) Shoba Khalid sey, wo eik shakhs sey, wo Abu-Tameema sey, wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se."
2212,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain ke ''bila-shuba Ibrahim Alehissalam ne kabhi jhoot nahin bola magar teen mawaqe par. do baar Allah azz-w-jall ke baarey mein . jabkey aapney ( qom sey) kaha tha ''main bimar hun"" ya ""meri tabiat naasaaz hai.'' dusri baar aapney kaha tha : ''ye to unke is badey ne kya hai.'' aur teesri baar jabke wo eik Jabir badshah ke ilaqey mein se ja rahey they ke eik jagah padaaw kya to us zalim badshah ko khabar di gaee aur kaha gaya ke yahan eik shakhs utra hai aur uskey sath eik aurat hai intehai Husain w jameel ! to usney Hazrat Ibrahim Alehissalam ko bula bheja aur khatoon ke mutalliq puchha to unhoney kaha : ''ye meri behan hai. aur jab wo apni ehliya ke paas lotey to usey bataya ke usney mujh se tumharey mutalliq puchha hai aur maine usko bataya hai ke to meri behan hai aur haqeeqat ye hai ke aaj terey aur merey ilawa koi musalman nahin hai aur Allah ki kitab mein to meri behan hai to mujhey uskey yahan mat jhutlana .'' aur hadees bayan ki . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke is hadees ko Shuaib bin abi Hamza ne abu-Zinad sey, unhoney Aaraj sey, unhoney Hazrat Abu-Huraira sey, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se usi ki manind riwayat kya hai."
2213,"Hazrat Salma bin sakhr Bayazi (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke main aisa shakhs tha jo aurton ko is qadr aata tha ke koi aur kya aata hoga. (badi jinsi quwat wala tha.) jab Ramazan ka mahina aaya to mujhey andesha hua ke biwi ke sath kuch kar na bethun ke subh tak alag hi na ho sakun. so maine us se zihar kar liya yahan tak ke Ramazan guzar jaey. ittifaq se eik raat wo meri khidmat kar rahi thi ke uskey jism ka kuch hissey merey samney zahir hua to main zabt na kar saka aur uskey ooper chadh gaya. jab subh hui to main apni qom ke paas gaya aur unhen apna qissa bataya aur unhen kaha : merey sath Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas chalo , wo kehney lagey : nahin, qasam Allah ki ! ( ham to nahin jatey ( to main khud hi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas hazir ho gaya aur aap ko khabar di. aapney kaha : '' Salma ! arey to ne?'' maine arz kya : haan aey Allah ke Rasool ! maine . ... do baar kaha aur main Allah ke hukm par sabir ( razi ( hun, merey baarey mein jo Allah aap ko sujhaaye faisla farma dijiye. aapney farmaya : ''eik gardan azad kar do ''maine kaha : qasam Allah ki jisney aap ko haq ke sath Nabi banakar bheja hai! main to bas usi ka Malik hun aur maine apni gardan ki eik janib par haath maara . aapney farmaya : '' to phir do mahiney mutawatir rozey rakho.'' maine kaha ke aur ye jo kuch merey sath hua hai, rozon hi ki wajeh se to hua hai. aapney farmaya : ''to eik wasq (saath saa) khajoor saath miskeenon mein taqseem kar do.'' maine kaha : qasam us zaat ki jisney aap ko haq ke sath Nabi banakar bheja hai ! ham ne to bhookey peton raat guzari hai, hamarey paas khaney ko kuch na tha. aapney farmaya : '' to bani zuraiq ke sadqa kerney waley ke paas chaley jao, wo tumhen kuch dega . to us mein se eik wasq khajoor saath miskeenon ko khila dena aur baqi tum aur tumhara ayaal kha ley.'' chunanche main apni qom ke paas wapis aaya aur unhen kaha ke maine tumharey paas tangi aur buri raey paai, jabkey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas se wusat aur behtareen raey mili hai. aapney mujhey tumharey sadqey (leney) ka hukm farmaya hai. ibne-al-Ula ne kaha : ibne-Idrees ne wazahat ki ke Bayaza, bani Zuraiq ki eik biradari ka naam hai."
2214,"Hazrat khuwela binte-Malik bin Solba (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke merey shohar Aus bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujh se zihar kar liya to main shikayat lekar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) mujh se us masley mein behes farmaney lagey . aap kehtey they : ''Allah se daro, wo tumhara chacha zaad hai. main wahan se na hati thi ke Quran nazil ho gaya :  قد سمع الله قول التي تجادلك في زوجها . . ۔ bayan kaffarey tak . ... . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' wo gardan azad karey. '' usney kaha : uskey paas nahin hai. aapney farmaya : ''wo do mahiney mutawatir rozey rakhey.'' usney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool! wo bahut boodha hai, rozey kahan rakh sakta hai? farmaya : ''to saath miskeenon ko khana khilaaey.'' usney kaha : uskey paas kuch nahin hai ke sadqa karey. bayan karti hain ke usi waqt aap ke paas eik tokraa khajoor ka aa gaya. maine kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! main eik aur tokrey ( khajoor ( se uski madad kar sakti hun. aapney farmaya : '' bahut behtar hai. jao aur uski taraf se ye saath miskeenon ko khila do aur apney chacha zaad ki taraf lot jao .) Yahya bin Adam ne ( kaha ke) العرق ( ) tokrey ( mein saath saa khajoor aati hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne us riwayat mein kaha ke us ( khatoon ( ne apney shohar ki taraf se uskey mashwarey ke baghair hi kaffara ada kar diya tha. aur kaha ke ye (Aus bin Saamit) Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) ke bhai hain."
2215,"ibn Is-haq ne isi sanad se mazkura riwayat ki manind riwayat kya magar kaha ke '' ( العرق) '' wo tokraa hota hai jis mein tees saa khajoor aati hai. Imam Abu-Dawud farmatey hain : ye riwayat , Yahya bin Adam ki) mazkura baala ( riwayat se ziyada sahih hai."
2216,abu-Salma bin Abdur-Rehman ne kaha : '' ( العرق ( '' se murad aisa tokraa hota hai jis mein pandarah saa khajoor aati hai.
2217,"Suleman bin Yasar ne ye khabar bayan ki aur kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas khajoor laee gaee, aapney ye usey de-di jo pandarah saa ke qarib thi aur farmaya : ''isey sadqa kar do.'' to usney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kya apney aur apney ghar walon se ziyada faqir logon par sadqa karun ? aapney farmaya : ''tum kha lo aur tumharey ghar waley .''"
2218,"Janab Ata Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) ke bhai Aus (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unko pandarah saa jau inayat kiye they, yani saath miskeenon ka khana . Imam Abu-Dawud bayan kartey hain ke Ata ki Aus se mulaqat nahin hai. aur ye ( Aus ( ehle-Badrr mein se they, unki wafat bahut pehley ho gaee thi. aur ye hadees mursal hai. muhaddeseen usey Auzaai se b-waasta Ata aur wo Aus se riwayat kartey hain."
2219,"Hisham bin Urwa se riwayat hai ke jameela Hazrat Aus bin saamit ki zojiyat mein thi aur Aus mein jinsi shehwat ka mada ziyada tha, jab un par uska ghalba hota to wo apni biwi se zihar kar liya kartey they. tu Allah taala ne unke masley mein zihar ke kaffare ka hukm nazil farmaya tha."
2220,"Hammad bin Salma ne Hisham bin Urwa sey, unhoney Urwa sey, unhoney Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se. usi ke misl riwayat ki hai."
2221,"Janab Ikrima ( maula ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ( se manqul hai ke eik shakhs ne apni biwi se zihar kar liya, phir kaffara ada kerney se pehley uskey sath hambister bhi ho gaya , uskey baad Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaya aur apna waqia bayan kya. aapney puchha : '' to ne aisa kyon kya ?'' kehney laga : maine chaandni mein uski pindliyon ki safedi dekh li thi. aapney farmaya : '' to phir ab us se door rehna yahan tak ke apna kaffara dey ley.''"
2222,"Janab Ikrima (Rahimahullah) se marwi (bayan) hai ke eik shakhs ne apni biwi se zihar kar liya , phir chaand ki chaandni mein uski pindli ki safedi dekhi to us se mujaamiat kar betha , tab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya, to aapney usko kaffara ada kerney ka hukm diya."
2223,"Janab Ikrima (Rahimahullah) Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) sey, wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey, usi ki misl bayan kartey hain, magar us mein) Ismail raawi ne ( '' pindli '' ka zikr nahin kya."
2224,Janab Ikrima (Rahimahullah) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain jaisey ke Sufiyan (bin Uena) ki riwayat mein zikr hua hai. ( 2221 . 2222 (
2225,"Imam Abu-Dawud farmatey hain ke maine Muhammad bin Esa ko ye riwayat bayan kartey suna, wo usey b-waasta Motamir Hakam bin Aban se riwayat kartey they aur us mein ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka zikr nahin kya. (balke Ikrima se riwayat ki hai, yani sanad mursal hai. Imam Abu-Dawud farmatey hain Husain bin Hurais ne mujhey us riwayat ki ye sanad likh bheji (jo ke musnad hai) hamen Fazal-bin Musa ne khabar di Maamer sey, wo Hakam bin Aban sey, wo Ikrima sey, wo ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se. unhoney (mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kya."
2226,"Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo aurat baghair kisi wajeh ke apney shohar se Talaq maangti hai us par jannat ki khushbu haram hai.''"
2227,"Umra bint Abdur-Rehman , Habiba bint Sehal ansaariya (Raziallahu anha) ke mutalliq bayan karti hain ke ye Hazrat Sabit bin Qais bin Shamas (Raziallahu anhu) ki zojiyat mein thi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Fajr ki Namaz ke liye janey lagey to aapney Habiba bint Sehal ko andherey mein apney darwazey ke paas khadey paya . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne puchha : ''ye kon hai? '' usney kaha : main Habiba bint Sehal hun. aapney puchha : ''kya baat hai? '' kehney lagi : main nahin aur Sabit bin Qais nahin ! yani apney shohar ke mutalliq kaha .) matlab ye tha ke ham dono ka ikhatta rehna mumkin nahin) phir jab Hazrat Sabit bin Qais aaye to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un se kaha : '' Habiba bint Sehal aai hai aur Allah taala ko jo kuch manzoor tha usney mujh se bayan kya. '' Habiba ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! jo kuch unhoney mujhey diya hai wo sab merey paas hai. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Sabit bin Qais se farmaya : '' us se wasul kar lo .'' chunanche unhoney maal ley liya aur phir wo apney ghar walon ke yahan beth rahi."
2228,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Habiba bint Sehal , Hazrat Sabit bin Qais bin shamaas ki zojiyat mein thi to Sabit ne usko maara aur uska kuch tod bhi diya, tab wo Fajr ke baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aai aur shohar ki shikayat ki . pas Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Sabit ko bulaya aur farmaya : '' us se kuch maal ley lo aur usko alehda kar do .'' unhoney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kya ye sahih hai? aapney farmaya : '' haan .'' unhoney kaha : maine usko mehar mein do baagh diye hain aur wo usi ke qabzey mein hain. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' wo dono ley lo aur usey alehda kar do .'' chunanche unhoney aisey hi kya."
2229,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka bayan hai ke Sabit bin Qais (Raziallahu anhu) ki biwi ne un se Khula liya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uski iddat eik haiz muqarrar farmaai thi. Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke is hadees ko abdur-Razzaaq ne Maamer sey, unhoney Amr bin Muslim sey, unhoney Ikrima sey, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mursal bayan kya hai."
2230,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Khula wali aurat ki iddat eik haiz hai.
2231,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Mughis ghulam they. kehney lagey : aey Allah ke Rasool ! merey baarey mein usko sifarish farma dijiye to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Barira ! Allah se dar , bila-shuba wo tera shohar hai aur terey bachey ka baap bhi hai. '' wo kehney lagi : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kya aap uskey baarey mein mujhey hukman irshad farmatey hain? aapney farmaya : '' nahin, mein sirf sifarishi hun. '' chunanche us ( Mughis (ke aansu uskey rukhsaaron par behtey they. ( wo rota phirta tha. ( to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : '' kis qadr tajjub ki baat hai ke Mughis ko Barira se kitni mohabbat hai aur usko us se kitna bughz hai. ''"
2232,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se manqul hai ke Barira (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka khawind kalay rang ka ghulam tha, jis ka naam Mughis tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Barira ko ikhtiyar diya tha. (apney shohar ki zojiyat mein rahey ya us se azad ho jaey (aur usey hukm diya tha ke iddat guzaarey ."
2233,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) Barira ke qissey mein bayan karti hain ke uska shohar ghulam tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Barira ko ikhtiyar diya to usney apney aap ko ikhtiyar kar liya . agar shohar azad hota to usko ikhtiyar na detey .
2234,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Barira ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ikhtiyar diya tha, jabkey uska shohar ghulam tha."
2235,Aswad bin Yazid Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se bayan kartey hain ke Barira ko jab azad kya gaya to uska shohar bhi azad tha. aur Barira ko ikhtiyar diya gaya to wo kehney lagi : main uskey sath rehna pasand nahin karti chahey mujhey us is qadr ( maal ( bhi kyon na dey diya jaey.
2236,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Barira ko azad kya gaya to wo Mughis ki zojiyat mein thi jo ke aal abi Ahmed ka ghulam tha, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usko ikhtiyar dey diya aur farmaya : ''agar wo tum se qarib ho gaya to tumhara ikhtiyar baqi nahin rahega .''"
2237,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hai, unhoney apney eik mamlook jodey ko azad kerney ka irada kya to unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se us baarey mein puchha , aapney hukm diya : '' aurat se pehley mard ko azad kerney se ibtida (shuruat) karna.'' nasar bin Ali ki sanad is tarah hai : ( akhbirni Abu-Ali الحنفي  عن  Ubaidullah ( ."
2238,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur main eik shakhs musalman ho kar aaya . phir uskey baad uski biwi bhi musalman ho kar aa gaee to us shakhs ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ye aurat bhi merey sath hi musalman hui hai. to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usko us (ke shohar ( ki taraf lota diya.
2239,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke zamaney main eik aurat musalman ho gaee aur phir nikah kar liya . uskey baad uska shohar bhi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aa gaya. usney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! main bhi musalman ho chuka tha aur usey merey Islam qubul kerney ka ilm tha. chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usko doosrey shohar se chheen kar (us ka nikah fasakh kara ke) pehley shohar ki taraf lota diya.
2240,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apni saahibzaadi Zenab ko) unke shohar ( abul-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) par pehley nikah hi se lota diya tha, aur koi naya ( nikah waghera) na kya tha. Muhammad bin Amr ne apni riwayat mein kaha ke aapney chhe saal baad) lotaya tha (aur Hasan bin Ali ne kaha : do saal baad ."
2241,Hazrat Haris bin Qais bin Umaira al-Asadi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke jab maine Islam qubul kya to merey yahan aath aurten thin . maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se uska zikr kya to aapney farmaya : ''un mein se chaar ko muntakhab kar lo. Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke hamen ye hadees Ahmed bin Ibrahim ne Hasheem ke wastey se bayan ki to (sahabi ka naam) Haris bin Qais ke bajaey Qais bin Haris zikr kya. Ahmed bin Ibrahim ne kaha ke yehi Qais bin Haris hi sahih hai.
2242,"Ahmed bin Ibrahim ne bayan kya ke ham se Bakr bin Abdur-Rehman, qazi koofa ne bayan kya, unhoney Esa bin mukhtaar sey, unhoney ibne-abi Leila sey, unhoney Hameeza bin Shimrzil sey, unhoney Hazrat Qais bin Haris (Raziallahu anhu) se mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani bayan kya."
2243,"Hazrat feeroz ( dailmi ( (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, wo kehtey hain ke maine kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! maine Islam qubul kya hai aur meri zojiyat mein do behney hain. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' un mein se kisi eik ko Talaq dey do .''"
2244,"Hazrat Raafe bin Sanan (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Islam qubul kar liya magar unki biwi ne Islam qubul kerney se inkar kar diya, ( jiski wajeh se un dono ke darmiyan alehdgi ho gaee ( pas wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aai aur kaha : meri beti ne abhi abhi doodh chhoda hai ya chhodney ke qarib hai. Raafe ne kaha : beti meri hai. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Raafe se kaha : '' eik taraf beth jao '' aur aurat se kaha : '' dusri taraf beth jao : '' aur bachi ko un dono ke darmiyan bitha diya. phir maa baap se kaha : ''tum dono usey bulao .'' ( unhoney bulaya ( to bachi apni maa ki taraf jhuk gaee . pas Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kaha : ''aey Allah ! is bachi ko hidayat dey .'' chunanche bachi baap ki taraf maael ho gaee to usi ne usko ley liya ."
2245,"Hazrat Sehal bin Saad Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke uwemir bin Ashqar Ajlani (Raziallahu anhu) Aasim bin Adi ke paas aaye aur kaha : aey Aasim ! batlao ! agar koi shakhs kisi ajnabi ko apni biwi ke sath paey to kya usey qatl kar dey? phir to tum usey bhi qatl kar dogey ya kya karey ? Aasim ! merey mutalliq us masley mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se maloom karo . chunanche Aasim ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se sawal kya to aapney uskey sawal ko napasand kya aur us par aeb lagaya, yahan tak ke Aasim ko , jo usney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna bahut hi giraan guzra . Aasim jab ghar lota to uwemir uskey paas aaya aur puchha : aey Aasim ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne tumhen kya kaha hai? Aasim ne kaha : tum merey liye koi khair ka baais nahin baney ho, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us sawal ko jo maine aap se puchha bahut napasand kya hai. uwemir ne kaha : qasam Allah ki ! main us se khamosh nahin reh sakta. mein khud aap se daryaft karunga . chunanche uwemir (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey jabkey aap logon mein bethey huey they. usney kaha aey Allah ke Rasool ! farmaiye ke agar koi shakhs apni biwi ke sath kisi ajnabi ko paey to kya usey qatl kar dey , tab to aap usey bhi qatl kar dalengey ya kaisey karey ? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne jawab diya : ''bila-shuba Allah taala ne terey aur teri biwi ke maamley mein Quran nazil farma diya hai. pas ja aur usey ley aa .'' Sehal ne bayan kya : chunanche un dono ne liaan kya to main logon ke sath Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke yahan betha hua tha. jab wo dono farigh ho gaey to uwemir ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! agar main usko apney paas rakhun to (us ka matlab hoga ke maine ( uski baabat jhoot bola hai. ( maine us par jhoot nahin bola hai) . phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke hukm deney se pehley hi uwemir (Raziallahu anhu) ne usko teen talaaqein dey den . ibne-Shahab ne kaha : chunanche liaan kerney walon ka yehi tariqa ho gaya. (ke liaan ke sath hi judai ho jaeygi .)"
2246,Hazrat Sehal bin Saad Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Aasim bin Adi se farmaya : '' aurat ko apney yahan rokey rakho yahan tak ke bacha jan ley.''
2247,Hazrat Sehal bin Saad Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke main unke liaan ke moqe par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke yahan hazir tha. meri umr us waqt pandarah saal thi. aur hadees bayan ki. us mein zikr kya ke phir wo hamila nikli aur bacha apni maa ki taraf mansoob kya jata tha.
2248,"Hazrat Sehal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) liaan kerney walon ke us waqiey mein bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us aurat ka khayal rakho, agar usney aisa bacha jana ke aankhen uski siyah huin, peeth bhari huey to mera khayal hai ke us ( uwemir ( ne sach hi kaha hai. aur agar usney aisa bacha jana jo goraa hua jaisey ke Wahra ho (chhipkalii ki tarah ka eik zahreela keeda, jiskey daain baain pehlu surkh dhaariyaan hoti hain, yani baamni) to mera khayal hai ke usney jhoot kaha hai.'' chunanche bacha paida hua to usi naa-pasandida keyfiyat wala tha."
2249,Hazrat Sehal bin Saad Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye khabar bayan ki to kaha ke pas bachey ko apni maa ki taraf nisbat karkey pukara jata tha.
2250,Hazrat Sehal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ne us waqie mein bayan kya ke us (uwemir (Raziallahu anhu)) ne aurat ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke samney hi teen talaaqein dey din. aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usko nafiz kar diya aur jo kuch Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke yahan kya gaya sunnat bin gaya. Sehal kehtey hain ke main us waqiey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke yahan hazir tha. chunanche baad mein liaan kerney walon ke beech yehi tariqa jari raha ke un mein alehdgi kara di jati thi aur wo phir kabhi ikhattey nahin ho saktey they.
2251,"Hazrat Sehal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur mein us waqt hazir tha jab dono miyan biwi ne liaan kya tha, meri umr us waqt pandarah saal thi. jab unhoney liaan kya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un mein tafriq kara di. yahan tak Musaddad ki riwayat mukammal ho gaee . magar doosron ( Wahab bin bayan, Ahmed bin Amr bin sarah aur Amr bin Usman ( ne kaha ke wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas hazir tha aur aapney liaan kerney waley miyan biwi ke darmiyan tafriq kara di to shohar ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! agar main usey apney paas rakhun to ( goya ( maine us par jhoot bola hai. Imam Abu-Dawud ne kaha : kuch raawiyon ne ( عليها (ka lafz zikr nahin kya.  Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke '' liaan kerney walon mein tafriq '' ke bayan mein Sufiyan bin Uena ka koi متابع ( مؤید ( nahin hai."
2252,Hazrat Sehal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) is hadees mein bayan kartey hain ke wo aurat hamila thi to shohar ne uskey hamal ka inkar kya. chunanche ladkey ko maa ki nisbat se pukara jata tha. aur phir virasat mein bhi yehi tariqa chal pada ke bacha apni maa ka waris banta aur maa apney bachey ki waris banti jitna ke Allah azz-w-jall ne uska hissey muqarrar kya hai.
2253,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kehtey hain ke eik Jumey ki raat ham masjid mein they ke eik Ansari shakhs masjid mein dakhil hua aur kehney laga : agar koi apni biwi ke sath kisi ajnabi ko paey aur uska izhar karey aur boley to tum log ( tohmat ki wajeh sey) usko kodey maaro gey ya agar qatl kar dey to tum usko bhi qatl kar dalo gey , ( qisaas mein) aur agar wo khamosh rahey to intehai ghaiz w ghazab ki baat par khamosh rehta hai. qasam Allah ki ! main is baarey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se zarur daryaft karunga . chunanche aglaa din hua to wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur aap se puchha aur kehney laga : agar koi shakhs apni biwi ke sath kisi ajnabi ko paey aur phir boley to aap usey kodey maarengey ( tohmat ki wajeh sey) ya agar qatl kar dey to aap usey kodey maarengey ( qisaas mein) aur agar khamosh rahey to intehai ghaiz w ghazab ki baat par khamosh rehta hai. to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Allah ! maamla wazeh farma dey .'' aur dua kerney lagey yahan tak ke liaan ki aayat nazil hui : ( والذين يرمون أزواجهم ولم يكن لهم شهداء (aur jo log apni biwiyon ko ilzam lagaeyn aur unke paas apney siwa aur koi gawah na hun. . . . . .'' chunanche yehi aadmi us aafat mein mubtala kar diya gaya , phir wo aur uski biwi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aai, dono ne liaan kya. mard ne chaar shahaadatein den ke Allah ki qasam ! main sacha hun aur paanchwen baar kaha : agar main jhoota hun to mujh par Allah ki lanat ho. phir jab wo aurat bhi usi tarah lanat ke liye tayyar hui to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se farmaya : '' ruk jao ( khayal karo .) magar usney inkar kar diya aur lanat ki bad dua kar di. jab wo dono chaley gaey to aapney farmaya : '' shayad ye bacha janegi jo kalay rang aur ghungariyaaley baalon wala hoga .'' chunanche wo paida hua to kalay rang aur ghungariyaaley baalon wala hi tha."
2254,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Hilal bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) ne apni biwi ko shareek bin Sehma ke sath muttahim kya. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' gawah lao, warna tumhari kamar par had hai.'' usney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! jab ham mein se koi shakhs kisi ko apni biwi par dekhay to bhala wo gawah dhoondney jaeyga? magar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmatey rahey : '' gawah lao , warna tumhari kamar par had hai. '' to Hilal kehney laga : qasam us zaat ki jisney aap ko haq ke sath Nabi nabi banakar bheja hai ! main yaqinan sacha hun aur Allah azz-w-jall bil-zaroor merey baarey mein kuch nazil farmaeyga jo meri kamar ko had se bari kar dega. chunanche ye aayaat nazil huin : ( والذين يرمون أزواجهم ولم يكن لهم شهداء إلا أنفسهم ( yahan tak ke (من الصادقين) tak pahunchey . phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) chaley gaey aur un dono ko bala bheja aur wo dono aagey . Hilal bin Umayya khadey huey aur gawahi di aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farma rahey they : ''Allah janta hai ke tum mein se eik jhoota hai, to kya tum mein se koi tauba karta hai? '' phir wo aurat khadi hui aur gawahi di aur jab paanchwen baar kehney lagi : '' mujh par Allah ka ghazab ho agar ye sacha hai. '' to logon ne us se kaha : ye qasam ( Allah ki lanat aur ghazab ko) wajib aur lazim kar deney wali hai. ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne kaha : aurat qadrey thithki (bolney mein jhijki) aur peechey hati, ham samjhey ke shayad ruju kar legi magar usney kaha : main apni qom ko hamesha ke liye ruswa nahin kar sakti. aur paanchwin qism ke alfaz keh daley. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey dekhna, agar usney bacha jana surmagin aakhon wala, bhari-bhari sirinon (pushton) aur moti moti pindliyon wala, to ye shareek bin Sahma ka hoga (jiskey sath usko muttahim kya gaya hai.'') chunanche usney usi tarah ka bacha jana. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar kitabullah ka faisla na hota to main usey nishane-ibrat bana daalta (us par had jari karta. Imam Abu-Dawud farmatey hain ke Muhammad bin Bishr ki ye riwayat yani hadees Hilal bayan kerney mein ehle Madina munfarid hain."
2255,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne jab liaan kerney walon se qasmen khaney ko kaha to paanchwen qasam ke waqt aapney eik shakhs se farmaya : '' us mard ke munh par haath rakho . usey kaho ye wajib kerney wali hai) Allah ke ghazab, lanat aur azab ko .)"
2256,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Hilal bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu)) apney ghar mein) aaye aur ye un afrad mein se eik hain ( jo jang tabuk mein peechey reh gaey they aur) jinki tauba Allah taala ne qubul farmaai thi. ye apni zameen par se raat ko ghar aaye to apni ehliya ke paas eik aadmi ko paya . usko apni aakhon se dekha aur apney kanon se suna magar usko daudaya nahin yahan tak ke subh ho gaee . phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaye aur kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool! main Isha ke waqt apney ghar walon ke paas aaya to maine unke paas eik aadmi ko paya. maine apni aakhon se dekha aur apney kanon se suna. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us khabar ko napasand kya aur aap par ye bahut giraan guzri. phir ye aayaten nazil huin : ( والذين يرمون أزواجهم ولم يكن لهم شهداء إلا أنفسهم فشهادة أحدهم . ... » aap se wahi ki keyfiyat door hui to aapney farmaya : Hilal khush ho jao ! Allah taala ne tumharey liye aasani farma di hai aur us uljhan se nikalney ki sabeel paida kar di hai.'' Hilal kehney lagey : yaqinan mujhey apney rab se isi ki umeed thi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' aurat ko bulwao .'' wo aa gaee to aapney un dono par ye aayaten tilawat farmaeyn, aapney un dono ko nasihat farmaai aur unhen bataya ke aakhirat ka azab duniya ke azab ke muqabley mein intehai sakht hai. Hilal ne kaha : Allah ki qasam! maine uskey baarey mein sach kaha hai. wo kehney lagi : yaqinan jhoot kehta hai. tab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''unke beech liaan karao.'' to Hilal se kaha gaya : shahadat do to usney chaar dafa kaha : Allah ki qasam ! main albatta sacha hun. jab paanchwen qism ki baari aai to usey kaha gaya : aey Hilal ! Allah se dar, bila-shuba duniya ki saza aakhirat ke muqabley mein bahut halki hai. aur ye ( paanchwen ( qasam tujh par Allah ke azab ko wajib kar deney wali hai. usney kaha : Allah ki qasam ! Allah mujhey is par azab nahin dega jaisey ke usney mujhey is par (jhutlaya nahin aur) koi saza nahin di hai. chunanche usney paanchwen qasam uthai aur kaha : mujh par Allah ki lanat ho agar main jhoota hun. phir aurat se kaha gaya ke qasmen uthao to usney chaar qasmen uthaain ke Allah ki qasam! ye aadmi yaqinan jhoota hai. jab paanchwin ki baari aai to usey kaha gaya : Allah se dar ja. bila-shuba duniya ki saza aakhirat ke muqabley mein bahut halki hai. aur ye ( paanchwin) qasam wajib kerney wali hai jo tujh par azab ko lazim kar degi. to wo eik lamhey ke liye thithki aur twaqquf kya, phir boli : Allah ki qasam! main apni qom ko ruswa nahin kar sakti aur paanchwin qasam bhi utha gaee ke Allah ka ghazab ho mujh par agar ye shakhs sacha ho. tab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un dono ke darmiyan tafriq kara di aur faisla farma diya ke bacha baap ki taraf mansoob nahin hoga , na us aurat ko tohmat lagai jaey aur na uskey bachey ko koi taana diya jaey. jis kisi ne us aurat ko tohmat lagai ya bachey ko taana diya to us par had hai. aapney faisla farmaya ke us aurat ke liye khawind par na rihaaish lazim hai na nafqa ( kharcha ( , kyonkey ye dono Talaq ke baghair alehda ho rahey they aur na khawind faut hua tha. aapney farmaya : ''agar uska bacha qadrey surkh baalon wala, halkay sirinon (pushton) wala, ubhri kamar wala aur bareek pindliyon wala hua to ye Hilal ka hoga aur agar wo gehuney rang ka, ghunghriyaaley baalon wala, khuley aur badey aazaa wala, bhari pindliyon aur sirinon (pushton) wala hua to ye uska hoga jiskey sath us par ilzam lagaya gaya hai.'' chunanche usney bachcha jana to wo gandumi rang, ghunghriyaley baalon wala, khulay aur badey aazaa wala aur bhari pindliyon aur sirinon (pushton) wala tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar qasmen na uthai gaee hoten to main usey had lagata. (ya nishane-ibrat bana deta. Ikrima ne kaha : ye bacha baad mein qabeela Muzar ka sardar bana tha magar baap ki taraf nisbat na kya jata tha."
2257,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne liaan kerney walon ko kaha : '' tumhara hisab Allah ke paas hai. tum dono mein se eik to jhoota hai. aur) shohar se kaha ke) tujhey us par koi haq hasil nahin raha .'' usney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! mera maal ? aapney farmaya : '' terey liye koi maal nahin. agar to sacha hai to wo uska badal hai jo to ne uski ismat ko halal kya. aur agar us par jhoot bola hai to wo terey liye aur bhi baeed tar hai.'' ( eik taraf tohmat lagaey aur us par mazeed ye ke maal bhi maangey.)
2258,"Janab Saeed bin Jubair kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se puchha ke koi shakhs apni biwi ko tohmat lagaey to . ... . ? unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne bani Ajlan ke eik jodey mein tafriq kara di thi (Uwemir aur uski biwi mein) aur farmaya tha : ''Allah hi khoob janta hai, tum dono mein se eik jhoota hai, to kya tum mein se koi tauba kar raha hai? '' aapney apni ye baat teen baar dohraai magar unhoney inkar kar diya. chunanche aapney un mein tafriq kara di."
2259,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke zamaney main eik shakhs ne apni biwi se liaan kya aur bachey ka inkar kya to aapney unke beech alehdgi kara di aur bachey ko aurat ki taraf mansoob kar diya. Imam Abu-Dawud farmatey hain ke Imam Malik (Rahimahullah) ye jumla riwayat kerney mein munfarid hain yani ( وألحق الولد بالمرأة (aur Yunus Zohri ke wastey, Sehal bin Saad se riwayat kartey hain ke shohar ne uskey hamal ka inkar kar diya to bachey ko aurat ki taraf mansoob kya jata tha."
2260,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke bano Fazara ka eik shakhs Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur kehney laga ke meri biwi ne bachey ko janm diya hai jo kalay rang ka hai to aapney farmaya : ''kya terey paas oont hain? ''kaha : haan . aapney puchha : '' unke rang kaisey hain? ''kaha : surkh hain. aapney puchha : ''kya un mein koi gehuney (ya siyahi maael ( bhi hai? '' usney kaha : haan , un mein siyahi maael bhi hain. aapney farmaya : '' tera kya khayal hai. ... wo kahan se aaye ?'' usney kaha : shayad unko kisi rag ne khincha ho. aapney farmaya : '' us bachey ko bhi shayad kisi rag ne khincha ho.''"
2261,Zohri ne apni sanad se mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani riwayat kya aur kaha ke wo shakhs apni baat kehtey huey bachey se inkar ka ishara kar raha tha.
2262,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke eik Earaab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur kaha : meri biwi ne bachey ko janm diya hai jo kalay rang ka hai aur mujhey us par tajjub hai. aur mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani bayan kya.
2263,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke jab liaan ke mutalliq aayat utri to maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jo aurat kisi qom mein kisi ghair ko dakhil kar dey, jo un mein se na ho to wo Allah ke yahan koi maqam nahin rakhti, aur Allah taala usey apni jannat mein hergiz dakhil nahin kerega. aur jis shakhs ne apney bachey ka inkar kya jabkey bacha uski taraf dekh raha ho, tu Allah taala us se hijaab farma lega aur awwaleen w aakhareen ke rubaru usey ruswa kerega.''"
2264,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Islam mein zinakari ka koi tasawwur aur maqam nahin, jis kisi ne jahiliyat ke dinon mein ye amale-bad kya ho to bacha uskey usba hi se mulhiq hoga. aur jo koi nikah sahih ke baghair kisi bachey ka da'wa karey (zina ki wajeh sey) to na wo baap us bachey ka waris hoga aur na wo beta us baap ka.''"
2265,"Janab Amr bin Shuaib apney walid ( Shuaib ( se aur wo apney dada ( Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ( se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne faisla farmaya ke aisa bacha jiskey mutalliq baap ki wafat ke baad daawa kya gaya ho jabkey baap apni zindagi mein uska muddai raha ho aur baad mein uskey warison ne bhi uska daawa kya ho to agar bacha aisi londi ke pet se ho, ke mubashrat ke roz wo us muddai ki milkiyat mein thi to ye bacha uskey sath mulhiq hoga, jiskey sath ilhaaq ka daawa kya gaya hai. aur maale-virasat jo ilhaaq se pehley taqseem ho chuka us mein us bachey ka haq na hoga magar baqi maanda main apna hissey paeyga. lekin agar us baap ne, jiski taraf laahiq kiye janey ka daawa kya ja raha ho, uska inkar kya ho to uskey sath mulhiq na hoga. aur agar bacha kisi aisi londi se ho jo us muddai baap ki milkiyat na thi ya kisi azad aurat se ho, jiskey sath usney zina kya tha to bhi uskey sath us bachey ko mulhiq na kya jaeyga aur na waris hoga. agar-che jiski taraf uski nisbat ki jati hai wo uska muddai bhi ho. aisa bacha waladuz-zina hoga, kisi azad aurat se ho ya londi se."
2266,"Muhammad bin Rashid ne apni sanad se us mazkur hadees ke ham-maani bayan kya aur mazeed kaha : ye waladuz-zina hoga aur apni maa ke ehl ki milkiyat hoga chahe koi hon, azad aurat ho ya koi londi. aur ye faisley Islam ke awwaleen daur mein huey they. aur jo maal Islam se pehley taqseem ho chukey , wo ho chukey ."
2267,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik din badey khush khush merey yahan tashrif laye . ... Usman bin abi Sheba ke alfaz hain. ... . ke aap ke chehre ke khutoot chamak rahey they. aapney farmaya : ''Aaisha! kya kuch maloom hua ke Mujazziz Mudliji ne Zaid aur Usama ko dekha jabkey wo dono eik chadar se apney sar dhaanpey (letey) huey they aur unke paon nangey they to Mujazziz ne kaha : bila-shuba ye qadam eik doosrey se hain. Imam Abu-Dawud ne kaha : Hazrat Usama siyah rang ke they aur Hazrat Zaid safed rang ke .
2268,"ibne-Shahab ne apni sanad se mazkura baala ke ham-maani bayan kya. Hazrat Aaysha ne kaha : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) badey khush khush merey paas tashrif laye. aap ke chehrey ki dhaariyaan chamak rahi thin. Imam Abu-Dawud farmatey hain ke Usama siyah aur Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) safed rang ke they. Imam Abu-Dawud farmatey hain : ( أسارير وجهه (ka lafz ibne-Uena ne yaad nahin rakha. Imam Abu-Dawud farmatey hain : (أسارير وجهه) ke alfaz ibne-Uena ki tadlees hai, jo ke unhoney Zohri se nahin suney balke kisi aur se suney hain. ye alfaz Leis waghera ki riwayat mein aaye hain. Imam Abu-Dawud ne kaha : Ahmed bin Saleh kaha kartey they ke Hazrat Usama (Raziallahu anhu) intehai kalay rang ke they jaisey ke tarkol ho aur Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) safed rang ke they jaisey ke rui."
2269,"Hazrat Zaid bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein betha hua tha ke Yamen ka eik aadmi aaya aur usney bataya ke teen Yamni Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaye. unka eik bachey ke baarey mein tanaaza tha. wo teeno kisi aurat par eik hi tuhur mein waqey huey they. Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne un mein se do ko kaha : apni khushi se us teesrey ke haq mein dast bardar ho jao, to wo dono cheekh padey (aur razi na huey .) phir unhoney doosrey do aadmiyon se kaha : apni khushi se us teesrey ke haq mein dast bardar ho jao. to wo razi na huey. phir unhoney doosrey do aadmiyon se kaha ke apni khushi se us teesrey ke haq mein dast bardar ho jao, to unhoney bhi inkar kar diya to Hazrat Ali ne kaha : tum baham (aapas mein) zid rakhney waley shareek ho. mein tumharey darmiyan qura daalta hun, jiskey naam ka qura nikal aaya bacha usi ka hoga aur us par wajib hoga ke apney doosrey sathiyon ko diyat ka teesra teesra hissey ada karey. chunanche unhoney un mein qura dala aur bacha usko dey diya jiskey naam ka qura nikla . us par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ( bahut ( hansay yahan tak ke aap ki daadhein numaya ho gaeen ."
2270,"Hazrat Zaid bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas teen aadmiyon ka maamla laya gaya jabkey wo Yamen mein aamil they, wo teeno eik aurat par eik tuhur mein waqey huey they. unhoney do se puchha : kya tum us teesrey ke liye bachey ka iqrar kartey ho? unhoney kaha : nahin! yahan tak ke unhoney sab se poochha. jab bhi do se poochhtey, wo nafi mein jawab detey to unhoney un mein qura dala aur bacha usko dey diya jiskey naam ka qura nikla aur us par do tihai diyat bhi lazim kar di. chunanche ye waqia Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke samney zikr kya gaya to aap us par hansey yahan tak ke aap ki daadhein nazar aaney lagen."
2271,khaleel ya ibne-khaleel se marwi (bayan) hai ke Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se us aurat ke baarey mein puchha gaya jisney teen mardon se bacha janm diya. (teeno ne us se sohbat ki thi) aur mazkura baala ki manind bayan kya. us riwayat mein Yamen ka ya Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka zikr nahin aur na ye hai ke khushi khushi bachey se dast bardar ho jao.
2272,"Urwa bin Zuber ne bayan kya ke ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne us (Urwa) ko khabar di ke jahiliyat mein chaar tarah ke nikah hotey they. eik yehi jo aaj (ehle-Islam mein) maroof hai ke eik insan doosrey ko uski zere-tauliyat ladki ke liye pegham bhejna hai, usey haq mehar ada karta aur phir us se nikah kar leta hai. dusri qism ye thi ke aadmi apni biwi se kehta, jabkey wo haiz se paak hoti ke falan ko pegham bhej do aur us se ja kar ham-bistar ho. phir uska shohar us se alehda rehta aur usey haath na lagata yahan tak ke uska hamal zahir ho jata jis se ja kar ye aurat ham-bistar hui hoti. jab hamal numaya ho jata to phir shohar bhi agar chahta to us se mubashrat kar leta. aur ye isliye kya jata tha ke bacha shujaa, zaki aur honhaar paida ho. us nikah ko '' ( نكاح الاستبضاع ( ''kaha jata tha. teesri qism ye thi ke eik jamaat . ... . das afrad se kam . ... ikhattey hotey aur eik aurat ke paas jatey, her eik us se sohbat karta, jab wo hamila ho jati aur bacha jannati aur bacha janne ke baad chand raaten guzar jatin to wo un sab ko bulwaati, aur un mein se koi bhi aaney se inkar na kar sakta tha. jab wo uskey paas jama ho jatey to wo kehti : tumhen apney maamley ka ilm hi hai aur maine bachey ko janm diya hai to ye bacha aey falan! tera hai. wo un mein se jiska chahti naam ley deti aur phir bacha us mard ke sath mansoob ho jata . chauthi qism ye thi ke bahut se log ikhattey hotey aur aurat par dakhil hotey , wo kisi ko bhi inkar na karti aur ye tawaifein hoti thin, unhoney apney khuwaishmandon ke liye bator alamat apney darwazon par jhandey lagaey hotey they jo bhi unka khuwaishmand hota unke paas chala jata tha, jab koi hamila hoti aur bacha janti to un logon ko ikhatta kya jata aur wo log apney liye kisi qiyaafa shanaas ko talab kartey, phir wo us bachey ko jiskey (mushabeh) dekhta, mulhiq kar deta aur wo uskey sath mansoob w mulhiq ho jata aur uska beta pukara jata, wo uska inkar na kar sakta tha. phir jab Allah taala ne Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Nabi banakar bheja to ehle-jahiliyat ke tamam nikaahon ko batil kar diya, sirf ehle-Islam ka mojud andaz nikah baqi rakha ."
2273,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Hazrat Saad bin Abi Waqas aur Abd bin Zam-aa (ye ummul-momenin Sauda (Raziallahu anha) ka bhai hai) apna eik jhagda Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas lekar aaye jo ke Zam-aa ki londi ke bete (ki tauliyat) se mutalliq tha. Saad ne kaha : merey bhai Utba ne mujhey wasiyat ki thi ke main (Saad) jab makkey jaun to Zam-aa ki londi ke bete ko dekhun aur usey apni tauliyat mein ley lun , bila-shuba wo mera hi beta hai. jabkey Abd bin Zam-aa ne kaha : wo mera bhai hai, merey baap ki londi ka beta hai, merey baap ke bistar par paida hua hai. chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne dekha ke bachchey aur Utba ke beech wazeh mushaabihat hai magar aapney farmaya : ''bachcha bistar waley ka hai, aur zaani ke liye patthar hain aur aey Sauda ! (Ummul-momenin (Raziallahu anha) ( is se parda kar.''  Musaddad ne apni riwayat mein kaha : ''aey Abd ! ye tera hi bhai hai.''"
2274,Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada se bayan kartey hain ke eik shakhs khada hua aur kehney laga ke aey Allah ke Rasool ! falan bachcha mera beta hai. maine jahiliyat mein iski maa se bad-kari ki thi to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Islam mein is qism ka koi daawa nahin chalta. jahiliyat ke umur (baaten) sab khatam hain. bachcha bistar waley ka hai aur zaani ke liye patthar hain. (ya mahroomi hai.) ''
2275,"Ribah ka bayan hai ke merey ghar walon ne apni eik romi londi se meri shaadi kar di. mein us se ham-bistar hua to usney bachcha jana , siyah rang ka , meri tarah . maine uska naam Abdullah rakha. mein phir uskey sath ham-bistar hua to usney kalay rang ka bachcha janm diya, jaisey ke main hun. maine uska naam Ubaidullah rakha . phir merey ghar walon ke eik ghulam yoohanna naami ne uskey sath kharabi ki, uskey sath apni romi zaban mein baaten kin. chunanche usney bachcha jana jaisey ke koi saam abras (girgit) ho maine londi se puchha : ye kya hai? usney kaha : ye yoohanna se hai. ham ne uska muqadma Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke samney pesh kiya. unhoney un dono se puchha to unhoney aetraaf kar liya. unhoney kaha : kya tum razi ho ke main tum mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) wala faisla karun? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne faisla farmaya hai ke bachcha bistar waley ka hai. raawi ne kaha mera khayal hai phir aapney un dono ko darrey (kodey) lagaey aur wo dono mamlook aur ghulam they."
2276,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke eik aurat ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! mera ye beta, mera pet iskey liye bartan , mera seena iskey liye mishkeeza aur mera daman iskey liye panah gaah raha hai. iskey baap ne mujhey Talaq de-di hai aur chahta hai ke usko mujh se chheen ley. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se farmaya : ''tu iski ziyada haq daar hai jab tak ke nikah na karey.''"
2277,"Abu Maimuna Sulmi, ehale-Madina mein se kisi ka maula tha aur wo sachcha aadmi tha. uska bayan hai ke main Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas baitha hua tha ke unke paas eik Farsi aurat aai , uskey sath uska beta bhi tha. shohar aur biwi dono us bachchey ke daawedaar they, aur shohar ne aurat ko Talaq de-di thi. aurat ne kaha aur Farsi zaban mein boli : aey Abu-Huraira ! mera shohar merey bete ko mujh se ley lena chahta hai. Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : is par quraa dal lo, aur isko ye Farsi mein kaha . phir uska shohar aaya to usney kaha : kon hai jo mujh se mera beta chheney? Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : (اللهم) (ye lafz bataur tabarruk bola jata tha) mera ye kehna is bina par hai ke maine eik aurat ko suna tha jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aai thi aur main bhi aap ke paas baitha hua tha, usney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! mera shohar merey bachchey ko ley lena chahta hai. halanke ye mujhey Abu Anba ke kunwen se pani la ke deta hai aur meri khidmat karta hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : is par quraa dal lo. to shohar ne kaha : mujh se mera beta kon chheen sakta hai? to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''(ladkey !) ye tera baap hai aur ye teri maa hai, jis ka chahey haath pakad ley.'' chunanche usney apni maa ka haath pakad liya , aur wo usey lekar chal di."
2278,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Hazrat Zaid bin Harisa Makka aaye aur Hamza ki beti ko sath ley aaye . to Jaafar ne kaha : main isey (apni tauliyat mein) leta hun, main iska ziyada haqdaar hun. ye merey chacha ki beti hai aur iski khaala meri zojiyat mein hai, aur khaala barabar maa ke hoti hai. aur Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main iska ziyada haqdaar hun. ye merey chacha ki beti hai aur merey ghar mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki saahibzaadiii hai aur wo iski ziyada haqdaar hai. aur Zaid ne kaha : main iska ziyada haqdaar hun. mein hi iskey paas gaya , safar kiya aur isko lekar aaya hun. phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye aur baat ki aur farmaya : ''ladki ka faisla mein Jaafar ke haq mein karta hun ke apni khaala ke paas rahegi aur khaala barabar maa ke hoti hai.''"
2279,Abdur-Rehman bin Abi-Laila ne ye riwayat bayan ki magar kamil bayan nahin ki aur kaha : aapney bachchi Jaafar ko de-di kyonkey uski khaala uskey yahaan hai.
2280,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke jab ham Makka se nikley to Hamza ki beti hamarey peechhey aa gaee , wo chacha chacha pukar rahi thi. isliye Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne usko liya aur uska haath pakda aur (Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) sey) kaha : apni chacha zaad ko ley lo. chunaanche Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ne usko utha liya . aur khabar bayan ki . Hazrat Jaafar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ye merey chacha ki beti hai aur iski khaala meri zojiyat mein hai. chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uska faisla khaala ke haq mein kar diya aur farmaya : ''khaala maa ki tarah hoti hai.''"
2281,Hazrat Asma binte Yazid bin Sakan Ansaariya (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hai ke unhen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke zamaney mein Talaq ho gaee. aur (is se pehley) mutallaqa ke liye koi iddat na hoti thi (yani ayyaame intizar) tu Allah taala ne is Asma ki Talaq ke mauqe par iddat ka hukm nazil farmaya. aur ye pehli aurat thi jiskey silsiley mein Talaq yafta aurat ki iddat ka hukm utra.
2282,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke) Allah ka jo farman hai) ''Talaq wali aurten teen haiz intizar keren.'' (to is se wo aurten nikal di gaeen jo haiz se mayus ho jaeyn) aur unke liye kaha ke ''tumhari jo aurten haiz se mayus hon, agar tumhen koi shubha ho to unki iddat teen maah hai.'' phir un mein se mazeed ye istisna farmaya : ''agar tum unhen masaas se qabl hi Talaq dey do to un par koi iddat nahin.'' (Al Ahzaab- 49)"
2283,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ko Talaq de-di, magar phir aapney un se ruju kar liya."
2284,"Hazrat Fatima binte-Qais (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hai ke (unke shohar) abu-Amr bin Hafs ne unko Talaqe-bitta de-di thi (mukhtalif oqaat (waqton) mein teen talaaqen) aur wo khud (ghar mein) maujud nahin they. to unke wakeel ne Fatima ki taraf kuchh jau bhejey to unhoney unko kam samjha aur is par razi na huin. to wakeel ne kaha : qasam Allah ki ! (kharche ke silsiley mein) terey liye ham par koi chiz wajib hi nahin hai. to wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aain aur aap se iska zikr kiya, aapney us se farmaya : ''uskey zimmey tumhara koi kharch nahin hai.'' aur usey hukm diya ke Umme- shareek ke ghar mein iddat guzaarey . phir farmaya : ''us aurat ke yahan merey Sahaba aatey rehtey hain, to ibne Umme-Maktum ke ghar mein iddat guzaaro. wo na-bina aadmi hai, tumhen apney kapdey utaarney mein bhi aasani rahegi aur jab tum halal ho jao (tumharey ayyaame-iddat (ke din) guzar jaeyn) to mujhey ittilaa dena.'' kehti hain ke jab main halal ho gaee to maine aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko bataya ke Muawiya bin Abi Sufiyan aur Abu-Jahm ne mujhey nikah ka pegham bheja hai. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Abu-Jahm to apney kandhey se lath hi nahin utaarta hai. aur Muawiya , to wo faqeer aadmi hai, uskey paas koi maal nahin hai. tum Usama bin Zaid se nikah kar lo .''kehti hain ke maine isko napasand kiya. aapney phir farmaya : ''Usama bin Zaid se nikah kar lo.'' chunanche maine un se nikah kar liya . Allah taala ne is mein bahut khair (aur barkat) farmaee aur is wajeh se mujh par rashk kiya jata tha."
2285,"Hazrat Fatima binte-Qais (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kiya ke Abu-Hafs bin Mughira ne mujhey teen talaaqen deen. aur puri hadees bayan ki, is mein hai ke Khalid bin Waleed aur bano Makhzoom ke aur bhi log Nabi karim (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaye aur kaha ya Rasulullah Abu-Hafs bin Mughira ne apni biwi ko teen talaaqen de-di hain aur bahut thoda sa kharch uskey liye chhod gaya hai. to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''uskey liye koi kharcha nahin hai.'' aur hadees bayan ki. aur Malik ki (mazkura baala) riwayat is se ziyada kamil hai."
2286,Hazrat Fatima binte-Qais (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kiya ke Abu-Amr bin Hafs Makhzoomi ne usko teen talaaqen dey deen. aur hadees bayan ki aur Khalid bin Waleed ki baat bhi. kaha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''uskey liye kharcha nahin hai aur na koi sukna hai.'' (shohar ke zimmey nahin hai.) is riwayat mein hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Fatima ki taraf paigham bheja ke apney baarey mein merey mashwarey ke baghair jaldi mein koi faisla na kar lena.
2287,Hazrat Fatima binte-Qais (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kiya ke main bani makhzoom ke eik shakhs ki zojiyat (nikah) mein thi to usney mujhey Talaqe-bitta de-di (teen talaaqen). aur (is baab ki pehli hadees) Malik ki riwayat ki manind bayan kiya. is riwayat mein kaha ke mujhey bataey baghair apney baarey mein koi faisla na kar lena. Imam Abu-Dawud farmatey hain ke Shobi (bhi) aur Ata ne ba-waaste Abdur-Rehman bin Aasim aur isi tarah Abu-Bakar bin Abi Jaham in sab ne Fatima binte-Qais se riwayat ki hai ke uskey shohar ne usko teen talaaqen di thin.  (in hazraat ki riwayat mein ''bitta'' ka zikr nahin hai.)
2288,Shobi Hazrat Fatima binte-Qais (Raziallahu anha) se bayan kartey hain ke unke shohar ne unko teen talaaqen di thin to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne iskey liye koi kharcha aur rihaaish (shohar par) lazim nahin ki thi.
2289,"Hazrat Fatima binte-Qais (Raziallahu anha) ne khabar di ke wo Abu-Hafs bin Mughira ki zojiyat (nikah) mein thi to usney isey aakhiri teesri Talaq dey di. phir wo kehti hai ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aai aur aap se puchha ke kya wo apney ghar se chali jaey (shohar ke ghar sey) to aapney hukm diya ke ibne Umme- Maktum na-bina ke ghar muntaqil ho jaey. magar Marwan ne Fatima ki is baat ki, ke mutallaqa (talaq paai hui) apney ghar se nikal sakti hai, tasdeeq kerney se inkar kiya hai. Urwa kehtey hain ke Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne bhi Fatima binte-Qais par inkar kiya hai. Imam Abu-Dawud ne kaha : Saleh bin Kaisaan, Ibne-Juraij aur Shuaib bin Abi Hamza sab Zohri se isi tarah riwayat kartey hain (jaisey Aqeel ne ki hai). Imam Abu-Dawud ne kaha : Shuaib ke walid Abu-Hamza ka naam Dinar hai jo Ziyad ka maula tha."
2290,"Ubaidullah (bin Abdullah bin Utba) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Marwan ne Fatima (binte-Qais) ko paigham bheja aur un se puchhwaayaa, to usney bataya ke wo Abu-Hafs ki zojiyat (nikah) mein thi aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko Yamen ke kuchh hissey ka aamil banaya, to uska shohar bhi unke sath rawana ho gaya aur usko Talaq ka paigham dey gaya, wo Talaq jo uski baqi thi (teesri Talaq) aur Ayash bin Abi Rabeea aur Haris bin Hisham ko keh gaya ke usko kharch dena, to un dono ne kaha : Allah ki qasam ! uskey liye koi kharcha nahin siwaey iske ke hamila ho. to ye Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas chali aai, to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''terey liye koi kharcha nahin siwaey iske ke to hamila ho.'' phir usney ijazat chahi ke (is ghar sey) muntaqil ho jaey to aapney usko ijazat dey di. kehney lagi : aey Allah ke Rasool ! main kahan rahun? aapney farmaya : ''ibn Umme-Maktum ke yahan.'' aur wo na-bina they, (kisi waqt) ye apney kapdey utaar bhi deti to dekh na saktey they. phir wo unke yahan rahi yahan tak ke uski iddat puri ho gaee . tab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Usama (Raziallahu anhu) se uska nikah kar diya. Qabisa Marwan ke paas wapis aaya aur ye sari khabar batai . to Marwan ne kaha : ham eik aurat se ye hadees sun rahey hain aur ham wohi mehfooz aur qabile-aitimad baat qubul karengey jis par logon ka amal hai. Fatima ko jab ye baat pahunchi to usney kaha : merey aur tumharey darmiyan kitabe Allah faisal hai : Allah taala ne farmaya hai : (فطلقوهن لعدتهن . . لا تدري لعل الله يحدث بعد ذلك أمرا) Fatima ne kaha : bhala teesri Talaq ke baad kon sa naya maamla hoga? (ruju ka mauqa hi nahin raha to naya maamla kaisey ho sakta hai. Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke ye riwayat Yunus ne bhi Zohri se isi tarah bayan ki hai. aur (Muhammad bin Waleed) Zubaidi ne dono riwaayaten bayan ki hain. Ubaidullah ki riwayat Maamer ke ham-maani aur Abu-Salma ki Aqeel ke ham-maani. Imam Abu-Dawud ne kaha : Muhammad bin Is-haq ne Zohri se riwayat ki hai magar is mein Qabisa bin Zuweb ne isko maana ke sath naqal kiya hai. iski daleel Ubaidullah bin Abdullah ki riwayat hai jis mein hai ke ''phir Qabisa Marwan ke paas wapis aaya aur ye sari khabar batai.''"
2291,"Abu-Is'haaq kehtey hain ke main Aswad bin Yazid ke sath (koofa ki) Jaame masjid mein baitha hua tha unhoney bayan kiya ke Fatima binte-Qais Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aai to Hazrat umr ne kaha : ''ham apney Rab ki kitab aur apney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki sunnat ko eik aurat ke bayan par nahin chhod saktey, na maloom usney yaad bhi rakha hai ya nahin.''"
2292,"Hisham bin Urwa apney walid se bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne is riwayat par bahut sakht aeb lagaya hai (inkar kiya hai), yani Fatima binte-Qais ki hadees par. aur kaha ke Fatima binte-Qais eik khaali makaan mein rihaaish pazeer thi aur us taraf se koi khatra sa bhi tha isliye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usko (ghar tabdeel kerney ki) rukhsat inayat farmaee thi."
2293,Urwa bin Zuber se marwi (bayan) hai ke Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se kaha gaya ke kya aap ko Fatima ki baat maloom nahin hui? to unhoney kaha : is baat ko zikr kerney mein uskey liye khair nahin hai.
2294,Fatima binte-Qais (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar tabdeel kerney ke silsiley mein Sulaiman bin Yasar se marwi (bayan) hai ke ''ye uski bad-khulqi ki wajeh se tha.'' (zaban ki tez thin)
2295,"Qasim bin Muhammad aur Sulaiman bin Yasar ka bayan hai ke Yahya bin Saeed bin Al-Aas ne (apni biwi Umra) binte  Abdur-Rehman bin Hakam ko Talaq de-di, Talaqe-bitta (teen talaaqen), to Abdur-Rehman ne apni beti ko (apney ghar) muntaqil kar liya. Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne Marwan bin Hakam ko paigham bheja aur wo un dino Madina ka haakim tha, ke Allah se daro aur aurat ko uskey (khaawind ke) ghar lauta do . Marwan ne kaha : (Sulaiman ke alfaaz mein) Abdur-Rehman mujh par ghalib aa gaya hai. aur (Qasim ke alfaaz mein) Marwan ne kaha : kya aap ko Fatima binte-Qais ka ahwaal nahin pahuncha? Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : agar aap Fatima ki hadees bayan na keren to aap ko koi nuqsan na hoga. (us ko eik khas wajeh se ijazat di gaee thi), Marwan ne kaha : agar aap eik shar ko intiqal ki wajeh jawaz samajhti hain to un shohar-biwi ke darmiyan mojud shar bhi iski wajeh jawaz hai."
2296,"Memun bin Mehran kehtey hain ke main Madina aaya to Saeed bin Musaiyab ke yahan pahuncha maine kaha : Fatima binte-Qais ko Talaq hui to wo apney ghar se muntaqil ho gaee thi , to Saeed ne kaha : us aurat ne logon ko fitney mein dala hua tha, bahut zaban daraz thi to usey ibne Maktum na-bina (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan rihaaish di gaee."
2297,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke meri khaala ko teen talaaqen de-di gaeen to wo apni khajuren kaatney ke liye nikal gaeen to usey eik aadmi mila jisney usko mana kiya. to wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aai aur aap ko ye baat batlaai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''chali jaya karo aur apni khajuren kaataa karo, tum is se sadqa ya koi khair ka kaam hi karo gi.''"
2298,Aayat kareema : (والذين يتوفون منكم ويذرون أزواجا وصية لأزواجهم متاعا إلى الحول غير إخراج) ''aur tum mein se jo log faut ho jaeyn aur apney peechhey apni biwiyan chhod jaeyn to (unhen chahiye ke) apni biwiyon ke liye wasiyat kar jaeyn ke eik saal tak unhen kharch dena hai aur ghar se nahin nikaalna hai.'' ki tafseer mein Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke ye hukm aayat meeras se mansookh hai aur unhen chautha ya aathwan hissey milega. aur eik saal ki muddat bhi mansookh hai aur ab uski muddat (iddat sirf) chaar maah das din hai.
2299,"Hazrat Zenab binte-Abi Salma (Raziallahu anha) (ye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki rabiba thin) ne ye nichey likhi teen hadeesen bayan kin. (Pehli hadees) : Zenab kehti hain ke main Ummul-momenin Hazrat Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan gaee jabkey unke walid Abu-Sufiyaan ki wafat ho gaee thi to unhoney khushbu mangwai jis mein zardi thi , wo khaluq thi ya koi aur, unhoney ye londi ko lagai phir apney haathon ko apney rukhsaaron par mal liya aur kaha : qasam Allah ki ! mujhey khushbu ki koi talab aur zarurat nahin hai magar maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna hai, farmatey they : ''kisi khatoon ke liye halal nahin, jo Allah aur aakhirat ke din par emaan rakhti ho, ke wo kisi maiyat par teen din se ziyada sog ka izhar karey (aur zeb aur zeenat chhodey rahey) siwaye shohar ke, (ke uskey liye) chaar mahiney aur das din hain. (Doosri hadees) : Zenab (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : main Ummul-momenin Hazrat Zenab binte-Jahash (Raziallahu anha) ke paas aai jabkey unka bhai faut ho gaya tha. to unhoney khushbu mangwa kar lagai aur phir kaha : qasam Allah ki ! mujhey khushbu ki koi talab aur zarurat nahin magar maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna, aap member par khadey farma rahey they : ''kisi aurat ke liye halal nahin, jo Allah aur aakhirat ke din par emaan rakhti ho, ke wo kisi maiyat par teen din se ziyada sog karey siwaey iske ke shohar ho to uskey liye (sog ke) chaar maah das din hain. (Teesri hadees) : Zenab (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : maine apni walida Ummul-momenin Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ko suna, bayan karti thi ke eik aurat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aai aur kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! meri beti ka shohar faut ho gaya hai aur ab uski aankh kharab hai, kya ham usko surma laga den? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''nahin.'' usney ye do ya teen martaba puchha . aapney her baar farmaya : ''nahin.'' phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye to sirf chaar maah das din hain jabke jahiliyat mein aurat eik saal guzarney ke baad mengni phenka karti thi. Humaid ne kaha : maine Zenab (Raziallahu anha) se puchha : mengni phainkney se kya murad hai? to unhoney bataya ke jab kisi aurat ka shohar faut ho jata tha to wo eik chhotey se gharondey mein rehti , bahut hi kharab kapdey pahanti aur khushbu to kya kisi chiz ko bhi haath na lagaati thi (tahaarat ke liye) yahan tak ke us kaiyfiyat mein saal guzar jata, phir koi janwer laya jata gadhaa, bakri ya koi aur parinda to wo usey apni sharmgaah ke sath mas karti aur phir aksar aisey hota ke wo jis chiz ko bhi sharmgaah ke sath mas karti to wo mar jati. phir wo bahir nikalti aur usey mengni di jati to wo usey phainkti thi. iskey baad jo wo chahti, khushbu waghaira istimal karti. Abu-Dawud ne kaha ke , hafsh'' ka maani gharondaa hai."
2300,"Hazrat Furaiyaa binte Malik bin Sanan (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hai aur ye Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ki behan hain, bayan karti hain ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui ke aap se ijazat lekar apney khandan bani Khadra mein chali jaaun kyonkey mera shohar apney un ghulamon ki talash mein gaya tha jo bhag gaey they. wo maqame qudoom ke atraaf (aas-paas) mein they ke merey shohar ne unko ja liya magar unhoney usko qatl kar dala, chunanche main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ijazat leney ke liye aai thi ke mujhey apney ehle mein laut janey ki ijazat den. kyonkey usney mujhey apney mamlooka makaan mein nahin chhoda tha aur na koi kharch hi bachaa gaya tha. bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne sun kar (pehley to) ijazat dey di. isliye main aap ke paas se nikli yahan tak ke jab main hujrey ya masjide-nabawi mein thi, aapney mujhey bulaya ya bulwaya aur farmaya : ''tu ne kaisey kaha hai?'' to maine apna qissa yani shohar ka waqia dobara dohraaya, to aapney farmaya : ''apney (shohar ke) makaan mein iqaamat rakh, yahan tak ke kitabe-Allah ki (bayan ki hui) muddat puri ho jaey.'' kehti hain : phir maine usi makaan main apni iddat puri ki, yani chaar maah das din. bayan karti hain ke jab Hazrat Usman bin Affan (Raziallahu anhu) ka daure-khilaafat aaya to unhoney meri taraf paigham bheja aur mujh se is masla ki tafsil daryaft ki aur maine unhen (tafsil sey) khabar di. chunanche unhoney usi par amal kiya aur usi ke mutabiq faisla kiya."
2301,"Janab Ata bin Abi Ribah bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne farmaya : ''aayat kareema (غير إخراج) ne aurat ke liye shohar ke ehle mein iddat guzaarney ko mansookh kar diya hai. so jahan chahey iddat guzaarey.'' Ata ne (is qaul ki wazahat mein) kaha : chahey to shohar ke ehle mein iddat guzaarey jaisey ke uskey liye wasiyat hai aur chahey to wahan se rukhsat ho jaey. kyonkey Allah taala ne farmaya hai : ( فإن خرجن فلا جناح عليكم فيما فعلن ( Ata kehtey hain ke phir aayat meeras nazil hui , isliye wo sukna mansookh ho gaya to jahan chahey iddat guzaarey."
2302,"Hazrat Umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aurat kisi (maiyat) par teen din se ziyada sog na karey, siwaye shohar ke. uskey liye chaar maah das din sog karey, koi rangin kapda na pehney magar wo kapda jiski bunai hi rangin dhaagon se ho (yamni dhaari daar chadar waghaira)  na surma lagaey na khushbu istimal karey magar haiz se tahaarat ke waqt maamuli qist ya azfaar ki khushbu istimal kar sakti hai. Yaqoob ne (asab) ki bajaey (maghsoola) ka lafz istimal kiya aur (ولا تختضب) ka izafa bhi kya. (mehndi na lagaey.)"
2303,Hazrat Umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anha) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se yehi (mazkura baala) hadees bayan karti hain magar ye riwayat puri tarah mazkura baala riwayaton ki riwayat ki manind nahin hai (Ibrahim bin Tahmaan aur Abdullah Sehmi ki riwayat ki tarah) Mismai ne kaha : Yazid ne bayan kiya ke mera khayal hai ke is mein (ولا تختضب) bhi hai (mehndi na lagaey). jabkey Harun ne izafa kiya ke ''rangin kapda na pehney siwaey iske ke uski bunai hi rangin dhaagon se ho.'' (jaisey ke yamni dhaari daar chadaren hoti thin.)
2304,"Ummul-Momenin Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis aurat ka shohar faut ho jaey, wo Asfar ( Zaafran (ya gairu rang ke kapdey na pehney. na zewar istimal karey, na mehndi lagaey aur na surma.''"
2305,"Umme-Hakeem binte Usaid apni walida se riwayat karti hain ke uska shohar faut ho gaya aur uski aankhen kharab rehti thin aur usney (جلاء) surma istimal karna chaha. Ahmed bin Saleh ne kaha : sahih riwayat (كحل الجلاء) hai. to usney apni khaadima ko Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ke paas bheja aur (كحل الجلاء) ''roshni deney wala surma'' istimal kerney ke mutalliq poochha. unhoney kaha : istimal na karey siwaey iske ke intehai majboori ho to raat ko istimal karey aur din mein saaf kar dey. ye khabar batatey huey phir Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : Abu-Salma ki wafat ke mauqe par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) merey yahan tashrif laye aur maine apni aankh par ailwa laga rakha tha. aapney kaha : ''Umme-Salma ! ye kya hai? '' maine kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ye ailwa hai aur is mein koi khushbu nahin hai. aapney farmaya : ''be-shak ye chehrey ko muzayyan (achchha) kar deta hai, lihaza sirf raat ko istimal karo aur din mein isey saaf kar diya karo. aur kisi khushbu wali chiz ke sath aur mehndi ke sath kanghi na karo (sar na dho) kyonkey ye khizaab hai.'' maine puchha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! to phir kis chiz se main kanghi kiya karun ? aapney farmaya : ''beri (ke patton) sey, usey apney sar par chipad liya karo (baad mein dho dala karo).''"
2306,"Ubaidullah bin Abdullah bin Utba ka bayan hai ke uskey walid ne umr bin Abdullah bin Arqam Zohri ko khat likha aur usey hukm diya ke Sabeeaa binte Haris Aslamiya (Raziallahu anha) ke paas jaey aur us se uska qissa daryaft karey aur ye ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey kya farmaya tha, jab usney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se masla puchha tha? chunanche umr bin Abdullah ne , Abdullah bin Utba ko likh bheja ke Sabeeaa ne bataya ke wo Saad bin Khaula ki zojiyat (nikah) mein thi jo ke qabeela bani Aamir bin looyi mein se they. ghazwae-badar mein shareek huey they aur Hajjatul-wadaa ke moqe par unki wafat hui thi aur un dino wo hamal se thi. unki wafat ke baad chand hi roz guzrey they ke bachchey ki wiladat ho gaee . jab nifaas ke dinon se paak hui to nikah ka paigham laney walon ke liye unhoney zeb aur zeenat shuru kar di. chunanche bano Abduddaar ka eik shakhs Abu-Sanaabil bin Ba'kak iskey paas aaya aur is se kaha : kya wajeh hai to ne zeb aur zeenat kar rakhi hai, shayad to nikah karna chahti hai? Allah ki qasam ! to us waqt tak nikah nahin kar sakti jab tak chaar maah das din na guzar jaeyn. Sabeeaa ne kaha : jab usney mujhey ye kaha to shaam ko maine apney kapdey lapetey aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho gaee aur aap se is baarey mein daryaft kiya. aapney mujh se farmaya : ''jab wiladat ho gaee hai to to halal hai.'' aur aapney mujh se farmaya : ''agar main chahun to nikah kar sakti hun.'' ibne-Shahab Zohri kehtey hain : '' waza'' hamal ke baad (bachche ke paidaaish ke baad) mein aisi aurat ke nikah mein koi harj nahin samajhta hun chahey khoon ke dinon hi hon, siwaey iske ke shohar tahaarat (paakizgi) se pehley uskey qarib na ho."
2307,Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke jo chahey mein us se mubaahala kar sakta hun ke chhoti sura nisaa (Sura Talaq) chaar maah das din (ke sabiqa hukm) ke baad hi nazil hui thi. (ye hukm sura baqara ki aayat : 234 mein waarid hua hai.)
2308,Hazrat Amr bin Al-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke ham par aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki sunnat ko khalt-malt mat karo. ibne Musanna ne kaha : hamarey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki sunnat ko . ... jis aurat ka khawind faut ho jaey uski iddat chaar maah das din hai. yani umme-walad (unki murad ye thi ke aurat chahey azad ho ya umme-walad sab ke liye hukm eik hi hai.)
2309,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha gaya ke eik shakhs ne apni biwi ko Talaq de-di yani teen talaaqen. phir us aurat ne kisi aur shakhs se nikah kar liya, wo is par dakhil hua magar mubashrat se qabl hi usko Talaq de-di, to kya ye pehley shohar ke liye halal hai? kehti hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye aurat pehley ke liye halal nahin yahan tak ke (aurat) kisi doosrey (mard) ki mithaas chakh ley aur wo mard us (aurat) ki mithaas chakh ley.''"
2310,Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke maine kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kon sa gunah sab se bada hai? aapney farmaya : ''ye ke tu Allah ke sath uska shareek banaey halanke usney tujhey paida kiya hai.'' kehtey hain : maine kaha : phir kon sa? aapney farmaya : ''ye ke to apney bachchey ko us dar se qatl kar dey ke wo terey sath mil kar khaye ga.'' kehtey hain : (maine kaha :) phir kon sa? aapney farmaya : ''ye ke to apney hamsaaey ki biwi se bad-kari karey.'' kehtey hain ke Shan Wale Allah ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke farman ki tasdeeq mein ye aayat nazil farmae (والذين لا يدعون مع الله إلها آخر ولا يقتلون النفس التي حرم الله إلا بالحق ولا يزنون) ''(Rehman ke bandey wohi hain) jo Allah ke sath kisi aur ko nahin pukartey aur na Allah ki haram karda kisi jaan ko qatl kartey hain magar haq ke sath aur na bad-kari kartey hain.''
2311,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah se riwayat hai ke Musaika eik Ansari ki londi thi, wo aai aur kaha : mera Malik mujhey bad-kari ke liye majboor karta hai. chunanche is silsiley mein ye aayat utri : (ولا تكرهوا فتياتكم على البغاء) ''aur apni laundiyon ko bad-kari ke liye majboor mat karo.''"
2312,Moatamir apney walid (Sulaiman Taimi) se bayan kartey hain ke aayat kareema : (ومن يكرههن فإن الله من بعد إكراههن غفور رحيم) ki tafseer mein Saeed bin Abi Al Hasan kehtey hain ke Allah taala ''majboor karda laundiyon ke liye maaf karne wala Raheem hai.''
